title: On his last day in office, relive President Obama's visits to Ann Arbor
text: From left, Michigan Gov. Jennifer Granholm, left, gives a thumbs up as President Barack Obama and Michigan president Mary Sue Coleman smile at the beginning of spring commencement at Michigan Stadium on Saturday, April 30, 2010.
